  "title": "Digital Marketing Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Scope:</strong></p><ul><li>Assist in planning and executing digital marketing campaigns across online platforms</li><li>Assist in photo / video taking for company events</li><li>Manage and update social media accounts and digital content (both graphical and video contents)</li><li>Support paid advertising campaigns (Google Ads, Meta Ads, etc.)</li><li>Assist with SEO, website updates, and content optimization.</li><li>Prepare marketing materials such as EDMs, simple visuals, and landing pages</li><li>Monitor campaign performance and prepare basic reports, if needed</li><li>Stay updated on digital marketing trends and platform best practices</li><li>Support consultant personal webpage</li><li>Any other ad hoc duties as assigned</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma or Degree in Marketing, Communications, Business, or related field</li><li>Minimum 1 to 3 years experience in a similar position, fresh graduates are welcome to apply</li><li>Basic understanding of digital marketing platforms and tools</li><li>Familiarity with social media platforms and online advertising</li><li>Knowledge of Google Analytics, SEO, or email marketing tools is an advantage</li><li>Added advantage of experience in: Wordpress / Elementor / JetEngine, Canva/basic design tools, DaVinci Resolve/Other video editing tools</li></ul><p><strong>Other Information:</strong></p><ul><li>5 day work week</li><li>Permanent position</li><li>Working hours: 9 am to 6 pm</li></ul>",
